{"tid":1944265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"( 賣港求榮 ) 梁偉雄坐正消防處處長 去年曾發表「曱甴」論","createTime":"2020-03-26T09:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T09:47:21.000Z","uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73736084f3b112b40270b3d1cccdf7b6fd06e4f8","tid":1944265,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/q-5Vcsr-u7nC44LMLGv6Xwm5yo0=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/3RAVFS36GRBO4G2ZACCHPPJ5WA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fq-5Vcsr-u7nC44LMLGv6Xwm5yo0%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F3RAVFS36GRBO4G2ZACCHPPJ5WA.jpg&h=485c9363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現任消防處副處長梁偉雄，將於下月18日出任消防處處長。<br />\n<br />\n消防處首長人事變動。去年曾發表「曱甴」論的消防處副處長梁偉雄，將於下月18日「坐正」，接替於同日展開退休前休假的李建日，出任消防處處長。<br />\n<br />\n政府今日公佈相關高層官員任命。公務員事務局局長羅智光形容，梁偉雄擁有豐富的部門運作經驗，並具備出色的領導和管理才能，深信梁能帶領消防處面對未來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n梁偉雄於1985年9月加入消防處任職消防隊長，於2013年十月晉升為副消防總長，於2015年7月晉升為消防總長，並於2016年8月出任消防處副處長至今。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">曾鬧示威者「曱甴」</span><br />\n去年10月，梁偉雄在內部講座上曾以「曱甴」稱呼示威者，做法引起爭議。處長李建日事後書面回覆議員，承認梁曾用「曱甴」形容「嚴重破壞法治和社會安寧，及罔顧法紀的暴徒」，同意用詞可能引起公眾一些疑慮，公眾觀感「並不最為理想」，處方將引以為鑑。<br />\n<br />\n至於即將退休的李建日於2016年8月出任消防處處長至今。消防處處長一般可工作至57歲才退休，在1965年出生的李建日，原可擔任處長一職至2022年，惟政府今日公佈有關任命安排，意味李建日提早約1年多退休。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/RIHRH4KJMR6WKUIP3SMALVOFZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FRIHRH4KJMR6WKUIP3SMALVOFZM%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR8rrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=fa00be21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FRIHRH4KJMR6WKUIP3SMALVOFZM%2F&h=02c01136\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/RIHRH4KJMR6WKUIP3SMALVOFZM/</a>"},{"pid":"e4a35764797fa2b87291ca7364267389ef33e17a","tid":1944265,"uid":41394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"建議一哥接管埋消防處、海關！ 實行做三軍統帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f5dca7299bcbda3ff39959cf4d5cfc33db06a0","tid":1944265,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"邊個做都係睇一哥頭"},{"pid":"be4fb407e2aaefdfc85d56250747eab5bad2f998","tid":1944265,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"發現屍體<br />\n<br />\n黑警：無可疑<br />\n消防：同意"},{"pid":"7148148088a87f600950b188f4dbcbb28d4fd95b","tid":1944265,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"香港曱甴論 好低沉<br />\n<br />\n如果有 &quot;50cent&quot;手足幫手 周圍屌人曱甴<br />\n<br />\n再帶香港人被稱曱甴事跡 應該會拍得住盧旺達"}]}